{"tid":2096073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國更新旅遊警示　籲在港公民避免觸犯「港區國安法」","createTime":"2020-07-06T02:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T17:37:00.000Z","uid":60281,"like":44,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f040c282524f0d731cd10126f51613d32ba0d81c","tid":2096073,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國外交部在最新的香港旅遊安全資訊指出，「港區國安法」對分裂、顛覆、恐怖主義和與勾結外國勢力等罪的「全新且含糊不清定義」，最高可處無期徒刑，而且在香港以外地區的外國人也可能犯法。<br />\n<br />\n德國外交部警告，在香港的德國公民應該格外小心，發表政治議論時要意識到可能的後果，即使在社交媒體發言也要注意。<br />\n<br />\n而德國工業聯盟指出，「港區國安法」將大幅擴大中央政府對香港的干預，讓原本已經緊繃的局勢更加惡化。<br />\n<br />\n德國工業聯盟表示，歐洲商人因為基本法承諾的言論自由等權利才在香港設置據點，這些權利如今不再，將增加商界的不安全感，呼籲中國落實實踐「一國兩制」，不要輕易失去國際公信力。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535996-20200706.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535996-20200706.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=2eb0726c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535996-20200706.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=724a95ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535996-20200706.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a163c6fb574623b2f4ada6ad899837e6a8984684","tid":2096073,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:09:30.000Z","msg":"又一國."},{"pid":"afcadac946e83ca2caea15f79b2c9cd8b9d018d9","tid":2096073,"uid":74171,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:11:11.000Z","msg":"石頭、腳已standby好<br />\n口交部出聲未？"},{"pid":"4e18c85b76ca852ba50442ae10d417f37333fbb2","tid":2096073,"uid":121146,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:13:17.000Z","msg":"德國連發個警示都仆街過人  乜原來屈你  係小心就避免到? 屌佢老母啦東德肥婆"},{"pid":"6e66a03ed65a3b85b886edac3a526c9924844e8f","tid":2096073,"